OL,3,GWest Midlands
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FAny early mist quickly clearing
OL,6,Fto leave a generally dry and bright
OL,7,Fday with plenty of sunny spells. An
OL,8,Fisolated light shower is possible in
OL,9,Fthe afternoon. Feeling very warm and
OL,10,Fincreasingly humid.
OL,11,
OL,12,CTonight:FAny showers easing to leave a
OL,13,Fdry night with clear spells and light
OL,14,Fwinds. Feeling warm and muggy,
OL,15,Fespecially in urban areas, bringing
OL,16,Fdifficult sleeping conditions.
OL,17,
OL,18,CMonday:FMostly dry and bright on
OL,19,FMonday with sunny spells for all. The
OL,20,Fodd light shower is again possible in
OL,21,Fthe afternoon. Feeling hot and humid.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
